com.github.wuic.util
Interface UrlProviderFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
UrlUtils.DefaultUrlProviderFactory
public interface UrlProviderFactory

This factory creates UrlProvider considering a particular workflow ID. Since the UrlProvider produces URL for a particular Nut, this factory gives a chance to include a workflow ID in a generated URL.
